           <span class="uitext reviewText">Anyone!</span></div>

        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer6616689" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7073842156852337207">This book literally changed my life! I read it when I was in Africa-- Ghana more specifically. I was really able to gain a perspective on life in West Africa, my own identity, and the political environment and fervor which creates acts of revolution. Everyone will find something amazing in this book. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


